# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Environment files and local secrets
#
# These lines are intentionally COMMENTED OUT so that .env files are tracked
# during the initial setup phase, allowing the team to review defaults.
#
# Once the project is stable and production secrets are in use, uncomment the
# lines below (or move them to per-package .gitignore files) to ensure that
# real credentials are never committed.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Uncomment these when you want to start ignoring local env files:
# .env
# .env.local
# .env.*.local
# apps/bugreport-api/.env
